---+!! Color scheme settings for %TWIKIWEB%.PatternSkin
Use this topic to change the color settings of %TWIKIWEB%.PatternSkin. When this topic is saved, the attachment =theme-colors.css= will be updated with new color values. This method relies on TWiki:Plugins.AttachContentPlugin to work.
d9 3
a11 2
Let %TWIKIWEB%.PatternSkin point to the custom-made colors style sheet. In [[%MAINWEB%.TWikiPreferences]] put: <verbatim>
   * Set USERCOLORSURL = %PUBURLPATH%/%TWIKIWEB%/PatternSkin/theme-colors.css
d18 1
a18 1
Save the topic. This will generate an [[%PUBURLPATH%/%TWIKIWEB%/PatternSkin/theme-colors.css][attachment]] to topic [[PatternSkin]].
d191 1
a191 1
%STARTATTACH{"theme-colors.css" web="%TWIKIWEB%" topic="PatternSkin"}%
